    "LLaMA and ChatGPT denote models without any fine-tuning.",
    "FT-All refers to fine-tuning on all datasets, FT-Per denotes fine-tuning separate models per dataset, and FT-Seq indicates fine-tuning on sequential datasets (D human → D vicuna → D llama → D chatgpt).",
    "w/ DELD represent baseline models with our method applied to detect various disinformation.",
    "Accuracy (%) for all models and datasets is shown, with higher values indicating better performance.",
    "We also provide the average accuracy across all four datasets for each model."
